  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge,chrome=1')
    title tweetstats &ndash; discover who among your friends are really worth following
    meta(name='description', content='discover who among your friends are really worth following')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles/style.css')

    body(id="top", class="page-#{page}")
      div(id="container")
        header
          h1 tweetstats

          - if (locals.user_id)
            nav Sort by:
              select(id="sort")
                option(value="tpd") Tweets per day
                option(value="dl") Days since last tweet
                option(value="t") Total tweets

              a(href="#", class="icon icon-bottom scroll") jump to bottom
              a(href="#", class="icon icon-top scroll") jump to top
              span |
              a(href="/logout", class="icon icon-logout") logout

            p(id="headline") Twitter friends most worthy of unfollowing will appear at the top of the list below, regardless of sorting order.

        div(id="body")
          block body

        footer by 
          a(href="http://twitter.com/erichynds/")@erichynds

